            <abstract id="ref2" label="Abstract">The Summit of the Americas was held in Quebec City, Quebec, in April 2001. The collection consists of ephemera related to the Summit.</abstract>
            <origination label="creator">
                <persname source="ingest">King, George, IV [collector].</persname>
