        <bioghist id="ref3">
            <head>History</head>
            <p>The Summit of the Americas was held in 
                <geogname>Quebec City, Quebec</geogname>, in April 2001.</p>
        </bioghist>
        <scopecontent id="ref4">
            <head>Scope and Content</head>
            <p>The collection includes publications, flyers, periodicals and a poster protesting the goals of the summit meeting.</p>
        </scopecontent>
        <arrangement id="ref6">
            <head>Arrangement</head>
            <p>Materials were filed according to size.</p>
        </arrangement>
