        </prefercite>
        <acqinfo id="ref10">
            <head>Acquisition Information</head>
            <p>The collection was donated to Archives &amp; Special Collections by Mr. King in May 2001.</p>
        </acqinfo>
        <relatedmaterial id="ref24">
            <head>Related Material</head>
            <p>Archives &amp; Special Collections has a substantial collection of materials documenting activities of organizations and individuals considered "alternative" to the mainstream of American culture, politics, society, and lifestyle. For detailed information on these collections please contact the 
                <extref ns2:href=" http://doddcenter.uconn.edu/asc/dodda2z/curatorinfo.cfm?curatorinfo=9">curator</extref> or ask at the Reading Room desk.</p>
        </relatedmaterial>
